latest la inks are always hard to find

Note that this new season is Season 4. When torrents of LA Ink were released in the past, people mistakenly labeled the second half of Season 3 as Season 4. So, there is bound to be confusion now.

Also of note is that Season 3 is hard to complete, it seems impossible to find all 24 episodes of Season 3 whether labeled properly or improperly. LOL
